title: Did a Group of Migrant Men With a Kidnapped Mexican Girl Hold a Texas Rancher in El Indio at Gunpoint?
subtitle: We sought to corroborate an incident described in a social media post that went viral in early 2019.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: A group of migrant men who had kidnapped and raped a Mexican girl held a Texas rancher in El Indio at gunpoint.
